# grapher_template_all_smoke.numos — Phase 9F. Insert all 6 templates (y=2x+3,
# y=x^2-4, sin, cos, x^3, 1/x) into 6 slots, plot together, screenshot. Proves the
# OpKind::Eq serialization fix makes every template plottable. Warning-only.
